Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:49.40,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(500,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}PAÍS DA AREIA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:49.40,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(500,0)}REINO DE ARABASTA
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.62,0:01:56.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos lá!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa é...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.09,0:02:09.74,Main,,0,0,0,,É a Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.74,0:02:11.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Boa viagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.37,0:02:12.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.79,0:02:14.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Sua Majestade!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Koza...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:27.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Parecia que Vivi-chan estava se divertindo muito.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:30.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela recuperou seu espírito pirata.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.18,0:02:32.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Justo quando eu pensei que ela estava começando a parecer uma princesa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.34,0:02:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, é a Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Acabamos de partir de Arabasta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:44.62,Main,,0,0,3,,Vamos escoltar a família Nefertari para Mary Geoise.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:45.47,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(500,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}VICE-ALMIRANTE DO \NQUARTEL GENERAL DA MARINHA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:45.47,OPLetreros,,0,0,0,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(500,0)}HINA, JAULA NEGRA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.62,0:02:47.46,Main,,0,0,3,,Hina-sama, aceite estas flores!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Nós as cortamos para você!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:50.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Não as quero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.40,0:02:52.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Jango!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:52.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Fullbody!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Vão para seus postos agora mesmo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.27,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.07,0:03:01.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.69,0:03:06.42,Main,,0,0,0,,É perigoso, Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.42,0:03:09.48,Main,,0,0,3,,Desça daí imediatamente!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:11.83,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(500,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}PRINCESA DE ARABASTA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:11.83,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(500,0)}NEFERTARI VIVI
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.48,0:03:11.92,Main,,0,0,3,,Vivi-{\i1}sama!{\i0}{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Que brisa marinha agradável...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.27,0:03:19.97,Main,,0,0,0,,E se aparecer um pássaro estranho e te sequestrar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:22.88,Main,,0,0,0,,E se um atirador de elite mirar em você?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Seria terrível se caísse um meteorito!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:27.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Você se preocupa demais.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Vivi-sama tem experiência como pirata.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Você ficou louco, Pell?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:36.05,Main,,0,0,0,,A Marinha está conosco!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:41.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Não exagere, Sua Majestade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:45.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Se você se sentir mal, voltaremos imediatamente.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.10,0:03:48.22,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, estou bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:52.10,Main,,0,0,3,,Desde o dia em que conheci Nico Robin,{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:56.15,Main,,0,0,0,,eu tive vontade de perguntar algo ao Governo Mundial!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:56.13,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(483,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}REI DO REINO DE ARABASTA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:56.13,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(483,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)}NEFERTARI COBRA
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:59.32,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Quando tudo o que eu quero é aprender sobre a história... {SC EP130 M16:11}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:05.05,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Há muitos inimigos dentro do meu sonho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:07.54,Main,,0,0,0,,É sobre os Poneglyphs?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.54,0:04:09.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:13.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou para esta Reverie, aconteça o que acontecer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.83,0:04:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Se possível, eu gostaria de saber...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:21.42,Main,,0,0,0,,...o que a família Nefertari fez ao mundo naquela época!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:27.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, não!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.85,0:04:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, não! Oh, não! Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:30.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:42.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Já chega, Vivi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:52.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Pai, como você está?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.65,0:04:55.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Não muito bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.50,0:04:58.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Talvez eu não viva muito mais.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:01.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Se minha filha se casasse logo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.28,0:05:05.45,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é justo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.45,0:05:08.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Você continua se aproveitando da sua doença!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.12,0:05:11.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos muitas fotos de pretendentes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:14.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Jogue-as fora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.67,OPLetreros,,0,0,175,,{\bord2.0\fad(278,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,540)}EAST BLUE - LOGUETOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:26.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Parabéns pela sua ascensão ao trono.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.03,0:05:32.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Nosso hotel existe apenas para as famílias reais que vão para a Reverie a cada quatro anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.68,0:05:35.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Esperamos que seja do seu agrado.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.01,0:05:42.73,Main,,0,0,3,,Não é nada mal.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.73,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(440,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}RAINHA DO REINO GOA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.73,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(440,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)}SALLY NANTOKANETTO
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é, querido?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:46.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, não tem nada de especial.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:51.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Só oferece uma boa vista da plataforma onde Gold Roger foi executado.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:55.29,Main,,0,0,0,,D-Descansem bem após sua exaustiva viagem,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.29,0:05:56.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Rei Sterry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.77,0:05:58.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, eles me incomodam.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:00.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Sumam, escória.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.51,Main,,0,0,0,,S-Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.51,Secondary,,0,0,0,,S-Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:15.85,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Há certa agitação nos países...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:18.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...por causa da Reverie,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.73,0:06:23.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,que ocorre na Terra Sagrada de Mary Geoise, no centro do mundo, a cada quatro anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:30.87,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nesta reunião de alto nível, líderes de cinquenta nações se reúnem...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:35.75,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...para discutir os assuntos de maior importância para o mundo...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:38.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...e estabelecer as ações a serem realizadas no futuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:44.05,Narrator,,0,0,0,,No entanto, por serem líderes prudentes e difíceis de lidar,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:48.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,as discussões geralmente não vão bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:55.62,Main,,0,0,3,,Don Chinjao, o líder da Armada Happo...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:59.86,OPLetreros,,0,0,173,,{\bord2.0\fad(529,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,540)}WEST BLUE - PAÍS DE KA
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:59.86,Main,,0,0,3,,Digo, Sai, o novo líder, \Nainda não voltou, certo?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.86,0:07:03.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Desde que o Chapéu de Palha e os outros derrotaram a Família Donquixote,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:06.82,Main,,0,0,0,,nosso inimigo não conseguiu obter armas.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:10.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Graças a isso, a guerra terminou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.15,0:07:13.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que poderemos ir à Reverie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.22,0:07:18.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Há muitas coisas que quero dizer!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:23.28,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(527,478)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}REINO RYUGU
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.96,0:07:23.28,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(527,478)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)}FUNDO DO MAR SOB O RED LINE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.60,0:07:27.55,Main,,0,0,0,,É impossível.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:28.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou com medo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.01,0:07:35.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama me prometeu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.86,0:07:38.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Quando eu o vir novamente,{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.25,0:07:42.05,Main,,0,0,0,,ele me levará a uma floresta \Nde verdade na superfície!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.98,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(526,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}PRINCESA DO REINO RYUGU
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:41.98,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(526,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)}PRINCESA SHIRAHOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:46.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro, Luffy-kun a levará \Npara lugares ainda mais distantes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas, desta vez, simplesmente iremos a Mary Geoise, que está logo acima de nós.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:57.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Seus irmãos e o exército de Neptune \Na acompanharão, princesa Shirahoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:07:58.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Céus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.85,0:08:04.06,Main,,0,0,3,,Pai, e se desta vez \Ndeixarmos Shirahoshi aqui?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:04.06,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(530,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}PRÍNCIPE DO REINO RYUGU
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:04.06,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(530,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)}RYUBOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:09.71,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(526,392)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}PRÍNCIPE DO REINO RYUGU
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:09.71,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(526,392)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)}MANBOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:04.95,Main,,0,0,3,,Sim!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.95,0:08:06.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Temos muitas assinaturas...{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.56,Main,,0,0,3,,...de pessoas solicitando a migração da Ilha dos Homens-Peixe!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.56,0:08:11.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Mambo!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:18.85,Main,,0,0,3,,Isso seria o mesmo que dizer que \Nnão confiamos nos humanos-yamon.{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:18.85,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(692,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}REI DO REINO RYUGU
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:18.85,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(692,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)}NEPTUNE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:20.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Que problema.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.72,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(538,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}PRÍNCIPE DO REINO RYUGU
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.72,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(538,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)}FUKABOSHI
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.74,0:08:24.72,Main,,0,0,3,,Shirahoshi, o que os Chapéus de Palha te ensinaram?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:28.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Esta reunião era o desejo \Nde Otohime, nossa mãe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos juntos!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:37.30,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(530,0)}SOUTH BLUE {SC778 T13:53}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:37.30,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(530,0)}REINO BLACK DRUM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Wapol-sama! {SC778 T16:18}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Tenho um relatório!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:46.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Dizem que o Reino Drum, que você governou, se tornou o Reino Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.27,0:08:49.55,Main,,0,0,0,,...e que seu rei, Dalton, irá à Reverie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.55,0:08:50.70,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.70,0:08:52.39,Main,,0,0,0,,O Reino Sakura, você disse?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Maldito seja, Dalton...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:59.44,Main,,0,0,0,,E se eu fizer com que ele perca \Nseu lugar na Reverie?!{\fad(0,1957)}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.62,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(489,0)}GRAND LINE{SC778 T5:22}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:05.62,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(489,0)}REINO SAKURA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:03.90,Main,,0,0,3,,O que você disse,{\an8} Doutora Kureha?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.62,Main,,0,0,0,,É sério?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.65,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(276,0)}REI DO REINO SAKURA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.65,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(276,0)}DALTON
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:08.65,Main,,0,0,3,,Por que parecem tão chateados?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.65,0:09:11.78,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu disse que serei a médica da sua viagem. {Vou mudar essa linha da SC, pois sem o contexto soa estranho, então ajustei para combinar com a versão do pace}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.78,0:09:13.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso te deixa feliz, não é?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.80,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(482,0)}DRESSROSA {SC778 T16:46}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:17.80,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(482,0)}O PAÍS DA PAIXÃO
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.24,0:09:16.20,Main,,0,0,3,,Hã?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.20,0:09:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Posso ir?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.80,0:09:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Que tal me acompanhar como minha criada?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:22.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu vou!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.00,0:09:24.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigada, Viola-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:26.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Você deve estar muito animada para ir, Rebecca!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:27.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:32.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Posso usar um dos vestidos da minha mãe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.86,0:09:35.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.65,0:09:37.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso seria ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.35,OPLetreros,,0,0,175,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(275,0)}REINO PRODENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.60,Main,,0,0,3,,Rei Riku!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.60,0:09:44.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Recusei a escolta da Marinha!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:47.02,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(527,0)}ELIZABELLO II
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.77,0:09:47.02,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(527,0)}REI DO REINO PRODENCE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.79,0:09:47.02,Main,,0,0,3,,Que tal irmos juntos para a Terra Sagrada?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:54.07,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)\fad(274,471)}RIKU DOLDO III
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:54.07,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)\fad(274,471)}REI DE DRESSROSA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.67,0:09:51.44,Main,,0,0,3,,Por que todos pensam que será um passeio?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.44,0:09:52.91,Main,,0,0,3,,O que há de errado?{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:57.31,Main,,0,0,3,,A Reverie é um festival!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.31,0:10:00.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Enquanto isso, o grupo de Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.06,0:10:02.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Um pouco a estibordo... {SC777 T19:17}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.78,0:10:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Que tal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:10.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, um pouco mais...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.25,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, ei, ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Façam com mais energia!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:15.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos afundar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.10,0:10:21.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Estamos todos assim porque \Nvocê pulou de repente do elefante!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.90,0:10:22.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:24.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigado.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:28.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora estou muito feliz por estar vivo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.88,0:10:31.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas você vai pagar por isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.07,0:10:34.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.53,0:10:37.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Perdemos o rumo de novo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,A bombordo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:44.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.02,0:10:44.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela está tão animada...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.96,0:10:49.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou realmente sobre o mar!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.93,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(480,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,480)}MOSQUETEIRA MINK
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.42,0:10:55.93,OPLetreros,,0,0,240,,{\bord2.0\fad(480,0)\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,710)}CARROT
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:55.93,Main,,0,0,3,,Este navio pesado está flutuando e se movendo!{\an8}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:58.97,Main,,0,0,0,,O que você está fazendo aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.76,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.76,Secondary,,0,0,0,,O quê?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Carrot?! {SC778 T1:42}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Carrot, o que você está fazendo aqui?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.76,0:11:15.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Vim com vocês!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:17.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Garchú!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Barão Cadáver!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.41,0:11:31.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Que difícil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:34.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, podemos dar meia-volta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:35.71,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Não façam isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Wanda vai ficar brava comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:42.84,Main,,0,0,0,,Você quer incomodar \Nnossos salvadores, Carrot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Só queria ter uma aventura no mar,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.73,0:11:50.10,Main,,0,0,0,,pelo menos uma vez na vida, com Luffy e os outros!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.10,0:11:52.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos nos infiltrar no território de uma Yonkou!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.80,0:11:54.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Não estamos brincando!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.02,0:11:57.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor, farei qualquer coisa, mas me levem!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.60,0:11:59.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Para não causar problemas...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Olhem!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.51,Main,,0,0,0,,Um almoço!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:03.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Suco!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:04.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Um lanche!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Roupas extras!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.37,0:12:09.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Quanto tempo você aguenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Meio dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:12.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas o mar é imenso, não é?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.72,0:12:15.20,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:18.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Vai levar muitos dias para chegarmos até Big Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:20.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Mesmo indo direto para lá?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.88,0:12:23.55,Main,,0,0,0,,Não acredito que seja tão grande!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:26.35,Main,,0,0,0,,O mar é uma terra fantástica!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.35,0:12:28.79,Main,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que durmo fora de casa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.79,0:12:30.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma terra?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:31.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas não é uma ilha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.89,0:12:33.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, não importa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:35.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Você já está a bordo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.36,0:12:38.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Você consegue se cuidar sozinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:38.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:39.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Obrigada!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou ficar bem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você está comendo minha cenoura?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:50.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Acaricie a cabeça dela, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:00.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Foi por pouco!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.33,0:13:01.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Quase me matou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.82,0:13:03.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Nada mal!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:05.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, vou te dar a cenoura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:07.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Quase derrotou o Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela é boa em lutar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:16.15,Main,,0,0,0,,Pedro-san, quando você subiu aí?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.15,0:13:18.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Você realmente gosta de lugares altos.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou com fome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.95,0:13:24.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos preparar a comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.37,0:13:26.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Alguém tem que fazer a comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,Que seja...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:33.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu farei, então fiquem de olho no mar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.98,0:13:35.40,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Certo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Ótimo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.07,0:13:40.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Serão cinco mil berries por cabeça.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:44.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere, espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:44.24,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Espere, espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos ficar sem dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.24,0:13:46.00,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Vamos ficar sem dinheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, o que faremos?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.17,0:13:52.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Teremos que preparar a comida, Brook ou eu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:53.42,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,É verdade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:58.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Se deixarmos o Luffy-san fazer, \Nquem sabe o que ele vai nos dar para comer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu farei!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.85,Main,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.75,0:14:01.85,Secondary,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:03.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixe comigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou preparar muita comida deliciosa!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.74,0:14:07.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Não, isso...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:09.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Qualquer coisa menos isso, espere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Comida, comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.54,0:14:13.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Espere, não faça isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.18,0:14:13.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:15.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Você sabe cozinhar?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.18,0:14:25.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Que manchete grande. {SC778 T20:10}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.82,0:14:32.78,Main,,0,0,0,,"A terra que por anos foi um mistério...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.25,Main,,0,0,0,,...finalmente foi revelada".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.58,0:14:43.15,Main,,0,0,0,,"Baltigo, o Quartel-General do Exército Revolucionário,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:45.66,Main,,0,0,0,,foi destruído".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.15,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2380,2880)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.15,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2380,2880)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.15,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2380,2880)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.15,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2380,2880)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:40.27,0:14:43.15,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2380,2880)}O Quartel-General do Exército Revolucionário foi revelado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:49.80,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.66,NDTBoard,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\1a&H80&\fad(300,0)\t(0,300,\fscx570)\move(133,65,133,-57,2380,2880)}Mola
Dialogue: 1,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.66,NDTSkull,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(60,69,60,-53,2380,2880)}Shi
Dialogue: 2,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.66,NDTHat,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2380,2880)}Chibukai
Dialogue: 3,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.66,NDTHat2,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\fad(300,0)\move(58,72,58,-50,2380,2880)}Fansub!
Dialogue: 4,0:14:48.79,0:14:50.66,NDTText,,0,0,0,,{\clip(0,0,1279,719)\alpha&HFF&\t(300,600,\alpha&H00&)\move(650,35,650,-81,2380,2880)}O Quartel-General do Exército Revolucionário foi revelado.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Derrotaram o Exército Revolucionário?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.88,0:14:56.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Se não me engano, você é o \Nfilho de Dragon, o Revolucionário...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.30,0:14:57.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.50,0:14:59.75,Main,,0,0,0,,É meu irmão!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.88,0:15:02.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Sabo-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:05.92,Main,,0,0,0,,O outro irmão com quem \Nvocê se encontrou em Dressrosa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.45,0:15:08.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele é o chefe de gabinete?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.40,0:15:11.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso significa que ele é \No número dois do Exército Revolucionário!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.82,0:15:14.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Que tipo de trio de irmãos são vocês?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.82,0:15:17.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, aquele Dragon que está ao lado dele...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:22.40,Main,,0,0,0,,É de quem seu avô falou há dois anos.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:25.30,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,O nome do seu pai é...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:27.47,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,...Monkey D. Dragon,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.47,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,771)}o Revolucionário.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:32.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Dragon, o comandante \Nchefe do Exército Revolucionário.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:35.33,Main,,0,0,0,,É seu pai!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele é meu pai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Agora que você percebeu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.64,0:15:43.14,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Agora que você percebeu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:44.95,Main,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que o vejo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:45.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.87,0:15:48.71,Main,,0,0,0,,O pai de Luffy é \No chefe do Exército Revolucionário?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.71,0:15:50.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Incrível!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:52.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Garchú!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:56.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Você não procurou informações \Nsobre ele nos últimos dois anos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:16:01.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Normalmente, qualquer um se preocuparia \Nem ter um pai tão famoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.20,0:16:04.18,Main,,0,0,0,,Além disso, ele cuidou da Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.18,0:16:05.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.16,0:16:06.64,Main,,0,0,0,,É a primeira vez que o vejo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.64,0:16:08.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas não nos parecemos muito.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:10.69,Main,,0,0,0,,Além disso, estou preocupado com o Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.69,0:16:12.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Caramba...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.10,0:16:16.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Bem, não é a mesma coisa ver ele em uma foto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:23.51,Main,,0,0,0,,"A localização do quartel-general foi revelada por um informante anônimo".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.51,0:16:26.88,Main,,0,0,0,,"No entanto, quando a \N Marinha e o Cipher Pol chegaram,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:31.00,Main,,0,0,0,,os Piratas de Barba Negra já \N tinham destruído o quartel-general".
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Barba Negra?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.92,0:16:35.43,Main,,0,0,0,,Malditos sejam!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:40.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas por que Barba Negra, um Yonkou, \N atacou o Exército Revolucionário?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.08,0:16:43.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Em Dressrosa, Sabo lutou...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.80,Main,,0,0,0,,...contra aquele tal campeão.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.80,0:16:46.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Será que foi por isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.64,0:16:58.95,Main,,0,0,0,,Parece que Barba Negra, o Yonkou, fugiu após enfrentar o Cipher Pol.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.95,0:17:00.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.87,0:17:04.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Além disso, ninguém morreu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:05.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.35,0:17:09.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Se seu irmão ou seu pai tivessem \N sido capturados ou mortos,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.48,0:17:11.27,Main,,0,0,0,,teria sido uma notícia importante.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:12.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:15.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Por enquanto, eles devem estar vivos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.72,0:17:16.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Entendi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.40,0:17:17.63,Main,,0,0,0,,Você tem razão!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.16,0:17:20.43,Main,,0,0,0,,O que há com você?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.43,0:17:24.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Acho legal que você queira \N cozinhar para nós, mas isso é normal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.06,0:17:26.99,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:31.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?! {na versão in pace dizia "fogo!" acho que a versão SC está correta aqui}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.60,0:17:35.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Droga!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.72,0:17:37.36,Main,,0,0,0,,Deixei o fogo aceso!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.36,0:17:39.44,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.80,0:17:42.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, explodiu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Apaguem o fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Esperem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:50.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Uma tempestade está chegando!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:52.75,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.31,0:17:56.44,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.44,0:17:58.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Electro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.76,Main,,0,0,0,,Amarrem as velas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:02.64,Main,,0,0,0,,O vento vai quebrá-las!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,E o incêndio?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:06.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Vai ser uma chuva torrencial!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:07.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Vai apagar o fogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:08.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Que sorte!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.79,0:18:10.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Não diga isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.86,0:18:19.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Trabalhe você também!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:22.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Estou à beira da morte!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.63,0:18:34.38,OPLetreros,,0,0,170,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(268,519)}ZOU
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.86,0:18:38.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, Carrot está no mar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.93,0:18:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Por que você não disse antes, Bariete?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.07,0:18:47.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, Wanda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:52.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu disse a Carrot que ela deveria avisar a todos.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.24,0:18:54.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas ela disse...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.20,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Não!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:58.52,Flashbacks,,0,0,0,,Se eu contar, eles não vão deixar!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela te subornou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.03,0:19:08.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Me pegou, hein?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:12.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas Carrot não estava tentando te trair...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.19,0:19:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.24,0:19:16.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz em saber onde ela está.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.41,0:19:19.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Estava preocupado que ela tivesse desaparecido.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.60,0:19:22.34,Main,,0,0,0,,Se ela está com Luffy e os outros, estará bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.92,0:19:36.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Duque, descanse, por favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.88,Main,,0,0,0,,Se quiser, posso colocar vigias.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.20,0:19:48.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Provavelmente, o inimigo tem uma Vivre Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.95,0:19:52.44,Main,,0,0,0,,Como eles conseguiram?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:59.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Espero que tenham perdido \Njunto com os navios que Zunesha afundou...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.49,0:20:02.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles vão voltar?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:08.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Precisamos ficar alertas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:42.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Venham rápido!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:51.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Me tirem daqui logo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:07.36,OPLetreros,,0,0,175,,{\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\pos(640,545)\fad(529,0)}EM CERTO PAÍS
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:15.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Como pensamos, Jack-sama \Nnão conseguiu resgatar o Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.16,0:21:24.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso significa que o acordo \Ndas Smile chegou ao fim...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:42.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,Hoje também ele será um bêbado chorão?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:50.68,Main,,0,0,0,,Então, não poderemos ter mais gifters!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.22,0:21:57.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.96,0:22:04.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Como foi que você foi derrotado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:13.07,Main,,0,0,0,,Você disse que criaríamos a tripulação pirata mais forte, composta apenas por usuários de Akuma no Mi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.43,0:22:24.99,Main,,0,0,0,,E ainda assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.96,0:22:35.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Você foi derrotado...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.64,0:22:40.32,Main,,0,0,0,,...por uns piratinhas iniciantes \Nantes de realizarmos nosso sonho?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:48.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Pobre Joker!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:51.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Foi por ser fraco!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:54.56,Main,,0,0,0,,Mas todos falam do Chapéu de Palha.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.56,0:22:55.72,Main,,0,0,0,,Se o subestimarmos...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:20.92,Main,,0,0,0,,Se o subestimarmos,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:23.21,Main,,0,0,0,,o que vai acontecer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:59.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem você acha que eu sou?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.20,0:24:03.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele virou um bêbado brigão!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.34,0:24:18.72,Main,,0,0,0,,K-Kaido-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Por favor, acalme-se!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.87,0:24:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Chapéu de Palha Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.96,0:24:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.12,0:24:38.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Eu sei!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.97,0:24:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles são dessa geração, certo?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.15,0:24:48.90,Main,,0,0,0,,São uns piratinhas que ficam arrogantes só por derrotar um Shichibukai!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.59,0:24:54.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Eles precisam saber que se meteram nos meus negócios!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.78,0:25:07.23,Main,,0,0,0,,Não incomodem!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.07,0:25:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, você!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.03,0:25:20.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Diga aos idiotas da sua geração!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.54,0:25:23.10,Main,,0,0,0,,"Fujam, rápido!".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.10,0:25:27.73,Main,,0,0,0,,"Tudo o que fizemos até agora \Nfoi brincar de piratas!".
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.80,0:25:38.41,Main,,0,0,0,,Eustass "Captain" Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.14,0:25:49.94,OPLetreros,,950,0,350,,{\fad(600,500)\pos(1130,390)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170}De volta ao\NThousand Sunny {este sinal foi adicionado no pace, então tive que traduzir eu mesmo}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.70,0:25:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, que frio!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.74,0:25:48.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Consertamos o telhado!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.74,0:25:48.46,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Consertamos o telhado!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.46,0:25:50.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, bom trabalho!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.02,0:25:51.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Muito bem!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.13,0:25:52.40,Main,,0,0,0,,A tempestade já passou!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.40,0:25:54.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Já consertamos o telhado que voou!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.64,0:25:58.30,Main,,0,0,0,,Guardei a comida que preparei, \Nentão vamos comer!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.30,0:25:59.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.26,0:26:00.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.30,0:25:59.26,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.26,0:26:00.13,Secondary,,0,0,0,,Comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.13,0:26:01.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Estamos com fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.40,0:26:07.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, está bom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.42,0:26:11.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Meu curry caprichoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.46,0:26:15.27,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy, não se pode comer arroz cru!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.27,0:26:17.76,Main,,0,0,0,,O que é isso roxo e amargo?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.76,0:26:19.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Está cheio de espinhas de peixe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.96,0:26:21.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Muita geleia!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.37,0:26:24.42,Main,,0,0,0,,Tem algo pegajoso e azul...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.42,0:26:27.44,Main,,0,0,0,,O que fizemos para merecer isso?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.44,0:26:31.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Que mal-educados, me esforcei \Nmuito para preparar isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.83,0:26:36.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Que nojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.89,0:26:37.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Viu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.90,0:26:39.91,Main,,0,0,0,,Não dá para comer!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.91,0:26:41.62,Main,,0,0,0,,Pare de se debater! {Não vire a mesa!}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.14,0:26:44.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Além disso, você desperdiçou comida!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.66,0:26:47.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji-san vai ficar bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.81,0:26:53.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Não temos mais ingredientes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.52,0:26:57.89,Main,,0,0,0,,Sim, usei tudo porque \Nerrei várias vezes!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.89,0:26:59.13,Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.13,0:27:01.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Era para durar uma semana!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.87,0:27:03.32,Main,,0,0,0,,Pensei que estariam com fome!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.43,0:27:06.05,Main,,0,0,0,,Não é para rir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.59,0:27:10.23,Main,,0,0,0,,O que vamos fazer?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.76,0:27:11.96,Main,,0,0,0,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.02,0:27:16.08,Main,,0,0,0,,Ei, estou com fome...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.08,0:27:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Sanji-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.80,0:27:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Socorro!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.16,0:27:27.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Assim, o grupo de Luffy ficou sem comida no primeiro dia de sua jornada.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.42,0:27:34.75,OPLetreros,,0,0,300,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(185,335)\bord2.0\fscx170\fscy170\fs24}Alguns dias depois,\NNavio da Big Mom {sinal adicionado no pace, então traduzi eu mesmo}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.42,0:27:34.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Navio, navio!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.36,0:27:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Pensei que fosse chuva...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.43,0:27:42.76,Main,,0,0,0,,É neve de algodão doce-soir!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.46,0:27:48.52,Main,,0,0,0,,Seu Den Den Mushi não para de tocar...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.24,0:27:52.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Estão recebendo sinais telepáticos de aviso-bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.79,0:27:56.21,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso significa que já estamos \Nno território da mama-soufflé.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.21,0:27:59.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Esses sinais telepáticos também chegam lá?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.00,0:28:00.86,Main,,0,0,0,,Como era de se esperar de você!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.86,0:28:03.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Essa é a Torta 28!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.09,0:28:09.89,Main,,0,0,0,,É uma subdivisão onde está um pelotão de piratas da Big Mom-millefuille.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.89,0:28:14.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Se este não fosse um navio da mama, \N já teriam nos atacado.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.51,0:28:19.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Já se decidiu?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.80,0:28:21.74,Main,,0,0,0,,Não seja tão teimoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.74,0:28:29.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Junto com o Germa 66, você vai se tornar parte dos Piratas da Big Mom-bon!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.02,0:28:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,Isso é o que seu pai deseja-amour.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.94,0:28:35.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Não fale dele!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.66,0:28:37.58,Main,,0,0,0,,Me dá nojo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.58,0:28:40.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Nossa relação acabou há muito tempo!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.91,0:28:50.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Só vim para acabar com isso!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.24,0:28:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,Não se gabe tanto.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.10,0:29:02.85,Main,,0,0,0,,Mamãe está de bom humor para recebê-los, \Nao contrário do que você pensa.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.85,0:29:08.53,Main,,0,0,0,,Claro, ela sabe que você é companheiro daquele idiota do Chapéu de Palha-plaît.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.53,0:29:13.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Ela te valoriza por ter sido cozinheiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.00,0:29:16.26,Main,,0,0,0,,...naquele restaurante marítimo no East Blue-bon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.24,0:29:22.97,Main,,0,0,0,,Seu tratamento depende de \Nquão bom cozinheiro você é-jour.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.97,0:29:24.73,Main,,0,0,0,,Não enche!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.73,0:29:25.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Escuta!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.66,0:29:30.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Essas mãos são para \Npreparar comida para meus companheiros!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.42,0:29:39.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Por isso treinei naquele inferno repugnante!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.67,0:29:50.29,Main,,0,0,0,,Me vêm à mente os rostos deles \Nchorando, sentindo falta da minha comida.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.06,0:29:52.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Que bobagem!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.26,0:29:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,Não tenho nada para cozinhar \Npara caras como vocês,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.14,0:30:01.74,Main,,0,0,0,,que ficam tranquilos mesmo quando \Natacam seu próprio companheiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.74,0:30:05.65,Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, está falando do Pekoms?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.65,0:30:08.66,Main,,0,0,0,,Ele deixou que seus sentimentos \Natrapalhassem seu trabalho.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.66,0:30:10.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Bege estava certo.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.14,0:30:14.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Barão Tamago...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.98,0:30:17.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Vito!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.54,0:30:22.38,Main,,0,0,0,,Nos enviaram de Whole Cake Island uma foto da Pudding-sama-rero!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.93,0:30:25.16,Main,,0,0,0,,Prepare-se.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.16,0:30:28.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Como sabem que é muito injusto casar-se com alguém que você nunca viu,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.80,0:30:30.80,Main,,0,0,0,,eles enviaram isso por pura gentileza.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.64,0:30:34.20,Main,,0,0,0,,Não faz diferença, idiota!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.20,0:30:36.02,Main,,0,0,0,,Quem vai se casar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.02,0:30:37.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Pelo menos dê uma olhada.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.67,0:30:39.26,Main,,0,0,0,,Cala a boca, não se aproxime!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.26,0:30:40.35,Main,,0,0,0,,Vou te chutar!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.35,0:30:41.79,Main,,0,0,0,,Vamos, não diga isso.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.79,0:30:43.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Que irritante...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.44,0:30:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,É com ela que você vai se casar.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.93,0:30:57.46,Main,,0,0,0,,A trigésima quinta filha da família Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.46,0:31:00.46,Main,,0,0,0,,Charlotte Pudding-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.73,0:31:03.83,OP11 Credits,,0,0,0,,Edição de vídeo:\NFeeso,\NGalaxy 9000\N\NControle de qualidade:\NBastia,\NFeeso,\NGalaxy 9000,\NGrug,\NPepperjack\N\NEdição de áudio:\NHalee\N\NTiming:\NLance\NUmim\N\NLegendas:\NJuanTlgd\N\NRevisão:\NRAFAEL
